### Create a Teacher
POST http://localhost:8080/teachers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "t1",
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "hourlyRate": 45.0,
  "aboutMe": "I have been teaching mathematics for over ten years in various schools."
}

### Get All Teachers
GET http://localhost:8080/teachers

### Get Specific Teacher
GET http://localhost:8080/teachers/t1